  "text": "The most significant finding in this paper is that a few nG field smoothed over k d,dec can easily produce y ≈ 10 −7 in the post-decoupling era. While y ≈ 10 −7 is small, it is well within sensitivity of the current technology, and a proposed experiment such as PIXIE would detect y ≈ 10 −7 at the 50-σ level [CITATION_1] . Therefore, such an experiment will be a powerful probe of the existence of intergalactic (possibly primordial) magnetic fields.",
